                <h2> <a href="../../../com/nutonian/blog/are-machines-partners-or-foes.html" id="hubspot-name" class="link hubspot-editable" data-hubspot-form-id="name" data-hubspot-name="Blog Title"><span id="hs_cos_wrapper_name" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_meta_field hs_cos_wrapper_type_text" data-hs-cos-general-type="meta_field" data-hs-cos-type="text">Are Machines Partners or Foes?</span></a> </h2>
